title: 1094 S Dearborn St #206 - OUTSIDE BALCONY & COMMUNITY POOL
posting_body: ['Text', 'show contact info', 'to setup a showing!', 'Virtual tour: 1094 S Dearborn St APT 206', 'AREA: Sunnyside Condos', 'FEATURES:', '**New carpet and paint**', 'Great condo packed with amenities such as a pool, AC, storage units, and fireplace.', 'Location is right near the Aurora Mall, Light-rail and Medical Center!', 'INCLUDED UTILITIES: Water & Trash!', 'TENANT PAID UTILITIES:', 'All other utilities paid by tenant.', 'BEDROOMS & BATHROOMS: 2 Bedroom and 1 bathroom all on the same floor', 'KITCHEN APPLIANCES INCLUDED: Refrigerator, Stove, Dishwasher, Garbage Disposal, Microwave', 'LAUNDRY: Washer and Dryer Hook-up', 'FLOORING:', 'Carpet and Laminate Flooring Throughout', 'HEAT/COOLING: Central Heat and Air', 'PARKING: 1 Reserved Spot #77', 'FENCING:', 'N/A', 'BASEMENT: None', 'RESTRICTIONS:', 'Pets considered with a one-time non-refundable pet fee of $250 per pet.', 'Sorry, but we cannot allow any of the following breeds of dog: American Pit Bull Terrier, American Staffordshire Terrier, and Staffordshire Bull Terrier.', 'SECURITY DEPOSIT:', "Security deposit is equal to one month's rent.", 'APPLICATION FEE: $30 per adult.', 'Please note we have a 700 minimum credit score for all properties.', 'AVAILABILITY DATE: Today!!', "**Applicants must be able to start a lease within 2 weeks of the property's listed availability date.", '**', 'LEASE TERM:', 'Initial leases are to end April through July of 2023', 'Growing marijuana inside or outside the premises is not allowed, smoking of any kind inside the property is not allowed.', 'Minimum 700 credit score required.']
